Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.95,0:22:04.50,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Donna aite mo ichi geki da!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.50,0:22:10.96,ED English,,0,0,0,,{Kara Romaji} Minna no negai mamoru tame...
